At
 
http://de.vivisimo.com/search?v:file=Microsoft
 
vivisimo.com, a search engine, is presenting a large categorized collection of Microsoft software patents. The 'web' category is particularly frightening.
 
Those are US patents. However, there is reason to be afraid that many - if not most - of these patents might already be granted in Europe with identical text.
